headline: A Look At Charles River Laboratories (CRL) Valuation After Planned CEO Transition And Governance Shift
summary: Charles River Laboratories International (CRL) has outlined a planned leadership change, with longtime Chair, President, and CEO James C. Foster set to retire in May 2026 and current COO Birgit Girshick appointed as his successor. See our latest analysis for Charles River Laboratories International.
